animeDescription: Norasco movies screen for the 9th Down Town Taito International Comedy Film Festival. 6 episodes of Norasco were scheduled to show with 2 of them being new creations never previously shown before. The first episode is the boys playing old maid and the second episode Kotarou's sister Michelle makes an unannounced visit.
